title: Age of (Streamed) GD Empires! GD vs. ChickenWrap (3v1)
body:
With Demon Sorceress, Takazaki, and notFREEfood joining forces, will it be enough to stop the wrath of the mighty ChickenWrap empire?

Well, there's only one way to find out, dear reader.

http://www.twitch.tv/hatchrawerberyl

(Thanks Powerburger for hosting the stream!)
